00:00:00.920 --> 00:00:04.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[OLD MAN 22A] The art of war
is an ever-evolving craft,</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:04.880 --> 00:00:08.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but you've taken a large step
toward unraveling its secrets.</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:09.300 --> 00:00:12.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The master's lessons have now
become the student's tricks.</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:13.470 --> 00:00:15.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That is what you
keep on telling me.</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:18.730 --> 00:00:21.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Oh, hey, it's Fern.
-[groaning]</b></Default>

c0000005
00:00:21.650 --> 00:00:23.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] She's about to erupt!</b></Default>

c0000006
00:00:23.270 --> 00:00:24.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But why?</b></Default>

c0000007
00:00:24.940 --> 00:00:25.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm scared.</b></Default>

c0000008
00:01:59.950 --> 00:02:02.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] Mistress Frieren
and I had an argument.</b></Default>

c0000009
00:02:02.670 --> 00:02:04.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't say I'm surprised.</b></Default>

c0000010
00:02:04.500 --> 00:02:06.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's been happening
a lot lately.</b></Default>

c0000011
00:02:06.960 --> 00:02:09.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Neither of you are in a place
to be wasting energy right now.</b></Default>

c0000012
00:02:10.130 --> 00:02:11.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The third test
is the final one, right?</b></Default>

c0000013
00:02:12.010 --> 00:02:14.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] This time,
she really crossed a line.</b></Default>

c0000014
00:02:14.720 --> 00:02:16.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At the very end
of the last exam,</b></Default>

c0000015
00:02:16.680 --> 00:02:18.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my staff broke during a battle.</b></Default>

c0000016
00:02:19.140 --> 00:02:21.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Obviously,
I told Mistress Frieren</b></Default>

c0000017
00:02:21.100 --> 00:02:22.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I wanted
to get it repaired.</b></Default>

c0000018
00:02:23.060 --> 00:02:25.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She said I would be better off
buying a new one.</b></Default>

c0000019
00:02:25.770 --> 00:02:28.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That it's destroyed,
and I should throw it away.</b></Default>

c0000020
00:02:28.400 --> 00:02:29.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm no staff expert.</b></Default>

c0000021
00:02:30.280 --> 00:02:31.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it sounds like she's saying</b></Default>

c0000022
00:02:31.530 --> 00:02:33.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when they're in pieces,
they're hard to save.</b></Default>

c0000023
00:02:33.570 --> 00:02:36.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000024
00:02:36.410 --> 00:02:38.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
I don't care if it's hard.</b></Default>

c0000025
00:02:38.280 --> 00:02:40.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Master Heiter
gave me that staff.</b></Default>

c0000026
00:02:42.870 --> 00:02:45.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's been with me
ever since I was little.</b></Default>

c0000027
00:02:47.000 --> 00:02:50.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're talking Frieren,
she didn't mean you any harm.</b></Default>

c0000028
00:02:51.010 --> 00:02:53.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] I know tact
isn't her strong suit,</b></Default>

c0000029
00:02:53.670 --> 00:02:56.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I never would have
even thought to throw it away.</b></Default>

c0000030
00:02:59.350 --> 00:03:02.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KANNE] Three years until
the next first-class mage exam.</b></Default>

c0000031
00:03:03.060 --> 00:03:04.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's a long time,
if you ask me.</b></Default>

c0000032
00:03:05.640 --> 00:03:07.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE] Go ahead
and make fun of me like usual.</b></Default>

c0000033
00:03:09.820 --> 00:03:11.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that what you want me to do?</b></Default>

c0000034
00:03:12.280 --> 00:03:13.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[LAWINE] No.
-Hm.</b></Default>

c0000035
00:03:15.360 --> 00:03:18.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Princess Lawine,
dost thou crave head pats?</b></Default>

c0000036
00:03:19.990 --> 00:03:22.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000037
00:03:22.910 --> 00:03:24.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps] Wanna fight?</b></Default>

c0000038
00:03:27.920 --> 00:03:29.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Make it quick.</b></Default>

c0000039
00:03:30.340 --> 00:03:31.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KANNE]
You're worse than I thought.</b></Default>

c0000040
00:03:34.840 --> 00:03:36.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, look, it's Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000041
00:03:41.850 --> 00:03:42.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000042
00:03:44.430 --> 00:03:45.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000043
00:03:45.520 --> 00:03:46.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's with the bag?</b></Default>

c0000044
00:03:48.600 --> 00:03:49.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] Hey.</b></Default>

c0000045
00:03:50.060 --> 00:03:51.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't need your company.</b></Default>

c0000046
00:03:52.820 --> 00:03:54.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I failed the test, remember?</b></Default>

c0000047
00:03:54.440 --> 00:03:56.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We no longer
have common ground.</b></Default>

c0000048
00:03:56.570 --> 00:03:59.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you're interfering
with my business.</b></Default>

c0000049
00:04:00.160 --> 00:04:03.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And here I thought businesses
liked having customers.</b></Default>

c0000050
00:04:04.080 --> 00:04:06.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you are shopping,
choose something.</b></Default>

c0000051
00:04:06.750 --> 00:04:08.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000052
00:04:08.710 --> 00:04:10.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[scribbling]</b></Default>

c0000053
00:04:10.840 --> 00:04:12.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Want some?
-Not at all.</b></Default>

c0000054
00:04:13.590 --> 00:04:15.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
You were unlucky this time.</b></Default>

c0000055
00:04:15.840 --> 00:04:17.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[scribbling]</b></Default>

c0000056
00:04:18.300 --> 00:04:20.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] You got the short end
of the stick.</b></Default>

c0000057
00:04:20.550 --> 00:04:22.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It could've happened
to any one of us</b></Default>

c0000058
00:04:22.140 --> 00:04:24.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and is no reflection
of your skill.</b></Default>

c0000059
00:04:24.720 --> 00:04:26.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A loss is still a loss.</b></Default>

c0000060
00:04:26.350 --> 00:04:28.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I simply wasn't strong enough
to beat it.</b></Default>

c0000061
00:04:29.480 --> 00:04:31.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] Don't bring
my failure up again.</b></Default>

c0000062
00:04:32.360 --> 00:04:35.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In case you couldn't tell,
I am in a horrendous mood.</b></Default>

c0000063
00:04:36.110 --> 00:04:38.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] And yet you still
opened your shop today.</b></Default>

c0000064
00:04:39.740 --> 00:04:41.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs] Now, Denken.</b></Default>

c0000065
00:04:42.240 --> 00:04:44.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know this may come
as a shock to you,</b></Default>

c0000066
00:04:44.410 --> 00:04:46.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but a man has to make a living.</b></Default>

c0000067
00:04:46.410 --> 00:04:49.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The race of life does not
slow down for our feelings.</b></Default>

c0000068
00:04:52.840 --> 00:04:54.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] Does it not?</b></Default>

c0000069
00:04:55.920 --> 00:04:56.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] Well...</b></Default>

c0000070
00:04:57.380 --> 00:04:59.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps it's for the best
that I'm the one who failed.</b></Default>

c0000071
00:05:00.380 --> 00:05:02.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It'll be three more years
until another exam.</b></Default>

c0000072
00:05:02.850 --> 00:05:06.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And truly...for an old man
such as you,</b></Default>

c0000073
00:05:06.430 --> 00:05:08.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>three more years
are hardly assured.</b></Default>

c0000074
00:05:09.680 --> 00:05:11.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
You're right about that.</b></Default>

c0000075
00:05:11.270 --> 00:05:12.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No fight left?</b></Default>

c0000076
00:05:12.940 --> 00:05:17.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000077
00:05:17.610 --> 00:05:18.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] Richter.</b></Default>

c0000078
00:05:19.030 --> 00:05:21.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You are undeniably
an impudent brat.</b></Default>

c0000079
00:05:22.410 --> 00:05:24.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You mock those above you
and have no qualms</b></Default>

c0000080
00:05:24.780 --> 00:05:26.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about mistreating
those below you</b></Default>

c0000081
00:05:26.490 --> 00:05:28.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if it helps you succeed.</b></Default>

c0000082
00:05:28.910 --> 00:05:31.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a challenge to find
anything admirable about you.</b></Default>

c0000083
00:05:32.710 --> 00:05:35.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yet for some reason,
I feel no resentment</b></Default>

c0000084
00:05:35.340 --> 00:05:36.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>toward you in the slightest.</b></Default>

c0000085
00:05:37.880 --> 00:05:39.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Probably because
at one point in my life,</b></Default>

c0000086
00:05:40.010 --> 00:05:42.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was a brat even
more impudent than you.</b></Default>

c0000087
00:05:44.510 --> 00:05:47.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But look at me now,
I'm an imperial mage</b></Default>

c0000088
00:05:47.350 --> 00:05:49.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and an accomplished member
of society.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:05:49.850 --> 00:05:51.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you trying to say?</b></Default>

c0000090
00:05:52.850 --> 00:05:55.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] I'm telling you
not to be so discouraged.</b></Default>

c0000091
00:05:56.070 --> 00:05:57.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In three years' time,
you'll be far stronger</b></Default>

c0000092
00:05:58.070 --> 00:05:59.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>than you are today.</b></Default>

c0000093
00:06:01.320 --> 00:06:02.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come along, Laufen.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:06:02.570 --> 00:06:06.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000095
00:06:06.370 --> 00:06:07.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Excuse him.</b></Default>

c0000096
00:06:07.620 --> 00:06:09.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Grandpa can't read a room.</b></Default>

c0000097
00:06:09.370 --> 00:06:11.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] This relationship
is getting strange.</b></Default>

c0000098
00:06:14.460 --> 00:06:16.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]
Damn it, old man.</b></Default>

c0000099
00:06:17.630 --> 00:06:19.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After all that,
he didn't buy anything.</b></Default>

c0000100
00:06:20.340 --> 00:06:21.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inhales deeply]</b></Default>

c0000101
00:06:21.970 --> 00:06:23.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]</b></Default>

c0000102
00:06:26.680 --> 00:06:27.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000103
00:06:28.760 --> 00:06:32.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000104
00:06:33.190 --> 00:06:36.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What did I do to deserve
such lovely patrons?</b></Default>

c0000105
00:06:36.310 --> 00:06:37.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I asked around town
for some help</b></Default>

c0000106
00:06:37.860 --> 00:06:39.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and was directed here.</b></Default>

c0000107
00:06:39.480 --> 00:06:41.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Rumor has it
you can fix any staff,</b></Default>

c0000108
00:06:41.240 --> 00:06:42.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>no matter how broken it may be.</b></Default>

c0000109
00:06:45.030 --> 00:06:46.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just show me.</b></Default>

c0000110
00:06:48.580 --> 00:06:50.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've brought me
a big pile of scrap wood.</b></Default>

c0000111
00:06:51.080 --> 00:06:52.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't say this is the staff.</b></Default>

c0000112
00:06:53.870 --> 00:06:55.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I fix things,
not dispose of trash.</b></Default>

c0000113
00:06:55.920 --> 00:06:57.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It is not trash.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:06:57.830 --> 00:06:59.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not for sure.</b></Default>

c0000115
00:07:00.670 --> 00:07:01.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000116
00:07:02.210 --> 00:07:03.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000117
00:07:03.470 --> 00:07:05.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My mood was finally
starting to improve,</b></Default>

c0000118
00:07:06.260 --> 00:07:09.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I fear you've launched me
even deeper into my spiral.</b></Default>

c0000119
00:07:10.970 --> 00:07:14.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have the right to choose
which jobs I accept.</b></Default>

c0000120
00:07:14.480 --> 00:07:15.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Give up on this staff.</b></Default>

c0000121
00:07:17.060 --> 00:07:18.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Fine.</b></Default>

c0000122
00:07:19.520 --> 00:07:21.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you can't do it,
then never mind.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:07:23.490 --> 00:07:24.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] Frieren...</b></Default>

c0000124
00:07:24.900 --> 00:07:26.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You test my patience
at every turn.</b></Default>

c0000125
00:07:28.700 --> 00:07:31.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I never said I couldn't do it,
now did I?</b></Default>

c0000126
00:07:33.080 --> 00:07:38.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000127
00:07:39.130 --> 00:07:40.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can you finish today?</b></Default>

c0000128
00:07:40.840 --> 00:07:43.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want it to be repaired
in time for the third test.</b></Default>

c0000129
00:07:43.710 --> 00:07:45.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're truly ridiculous.</b></Default>

c0000130
00:07:45.550 --> 00:07:50.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000131
00:07:50.600 --> 00:07:52.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[RICHTER] Frieren.
-Uh-huh?</b></Default>

c0000132
00:07:53.180 --> 00:07:54.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] I'm sorry
for calling it trash.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:07:56.690 --> 00:07:58.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a good staff
and well-maintained.</b></Default>

c0000134
00:07:59.690 --> 00:08:01.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Someone has clearly
taken great care of it.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:08:01.820 --> 00:08:04.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000136
00:08:04.400 --> 00:08:05.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chomps]</b></Default>

c0000137
00:08:06.150 --> 00:08:07.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[munching]</b></Default>

c0000138
00:08:07.410 --> 00:08:09.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>C'mon, Fern,
we should head on back.</b></Default>

c0000139
00:08:12.740 --> 00:08:14.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All this time,
and Mistress Frieren</b></Default>

c0000140
00:08:14.540 --> 00:08:15.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>doesn't understand me a bit.</b></Default>

c0000141
00:08:16.040 --> 00:08:18.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In her defense, I don't really
understand you, either.</b></Default>

c0000142
00:08:18.500 --> 00:08:20.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[groaning]
-Hey, I'm innocent!</b></Default>

c0000143
00:08:20.250 --> 00:08:21.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't take your rage out on me!</b></Default>

c0000144
00:08:24.260 --> 00:08:25.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What matters...</b></Default>

c0000145
00:08:25.630 --> 00:08:28.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is that she's always
trying to understand you.</b></Default>

c0000146
00:08:28.680 --> 00:08:30.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think she's
truly doing her best.</b></Default>

c0000147
00:08:31.050 --> 00:08:37.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000148
00:08:37.810 --> 00:08:38.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000149
00:08:39.020 --> 00:08:41.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] Look who it is,
Frieren's kid.</b></Default>

c0000150
00:08:43.070 --> 00:08:44.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're her student, right?</b></Default>

c0000151
00:08:45.900 --> 00:08:46.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000152
00:08:47.070 --> 00:08:48.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you not?</b></Default>

c0000153
00:08:48.530 --> 00:08:50.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] No, she is. Sorry.</b></Default>

c0000154
00:08:51.370 --> 00:08:53.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, thanks to your master,</b></Default>

c0000155
00:08:54.200 --> 00:08:56.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I got to have yet another
horrible day.</b></Default>

c0000156
00:08:57.200 --> 00:09:00.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's hardly been 24 hours
since I failed the second test.</b></Default>

c0000157
00:09:00.120 --> 00:09:01.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

c0000158
00:09:01.750 --> 00:09:04.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You could've saved my spirits
if you bought a new one.</b></Default>

c0000159
00:09:04.210 --> 00:09:05.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Put some more coin
in my pocket.</b></Default>

c0000160
00:09:07.800 --> 00:09:08.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Take good care of it.</b></Default>

c0000161
00:09:09.430 --> 00:09:10.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door creaking]</b></Default>

c0000162
00:09:10.970 --> 00:09:17.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000163
00:09:17.930 --> 00:09:18.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door closes]</b></Default>

c0000164
00:09:19.100 --> 00:09:24.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000165
00:09:25.110 --> 00:09:27.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She saved my staff. [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000166
00:09:27.780 --> 00:09:33.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000167
00:09:33.820 --> 00:09:37.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren's sharp, but she can
struggle to read emotions.</b></Default>

c0000168
00:09:37.830 --> 00:09:40.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I imagine that this will
cause many difficulties</b></Default>

c0000169
00:09:40.750 --> 00:09:42.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and disagreements
on your journey.</b></Default>

c0000170
00:09:43.460 --> 00:09:46.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It will prove tricky,
but there is an upside.</b></Default>

c0000171
00:09:46.920 --> 00:09:49.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She knows her weakness
and will worry about</b></Default>

c0000172
00:09:49.880 --> 00:09:52.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and care for you doubly so
to make up for it.</b></Default>

c0000173
00:09:53.930 --> 00:09:55.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Travel far and wide,</b></Default>

c0000174
00:09:55.930 --> 00:09:59.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but nowhere will you find
a better master.</b></Default>

c0000175
00:09:59.600 --> 00:10:00.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000176
00:10:04.360 --> 00:10:06.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

c0000177
00:10:06.650 --> 00:10:07.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Let's see.</b></Default>

c0000178
00:10:07.940 --> 00:10:12.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000179
00:10:12.450 --> 00:10:14.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

c0000180
00:10:14.660 --> 00:10:15.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Grimoire.</b></Default>

c0000181
00:10:17.120 --> 00:10:18.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind whooshing]</b></Default>

c0000182
00:10:22.710 --> 00:10:29.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000183
00:10:31.970 --> 00:10:33.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mistress? Real quick.</b></Default>

c0000184
00:10:34.550 --> 00:10:35.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry.</b></Default>

c0000185
00:10:36.180 --> 00:10:37.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>About what?</b></Default>

c0000186
00:10:38.600 --> 00:10:39.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000187
00:10:39.680 --> 00:10:42.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nothing,
you already understand.</b></Default>

c0000188
00:10:44.230 --> 00:10:45.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right.</b></Default>

c0000189
00:10:47.230 --> 00:10:48.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FALSCH]
Ready yourselves, mages.</b></Default>

c0000190
00:10:49.190 --> 00:10:50.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The third test will now begin.</b></Default>

c0000191
00:10:55.030 --> 00:10:57.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE] I wouldn't typically
make the journey here.</b></Default>

c0000192
00:10:58.160 --> 00:11:00.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Know why I did, Sense?</b></Default>

c0000193
00:11:00.790 --> 00:11:01.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SENSE] Huh?</b></Default>

c0000194
00:11:03.460 --> 00:11:04.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Opting for silence?</b></Default>

c0000195
00:11:05.460 --> 00:11:07.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Words always fail you
when trouble stirs.</b></Default>

c0000196
00:11:09.210 --> 00:11:12.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Twelve examinees
have passed the second trial.</b></Default>

c0000197
00:11:12.340 --> 00:11:13.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's completely unheard of.</b></Default>

c0000198
00:11:14.430 --> 00:11:15.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not right.</b></Default>

c0000199
00:11:16.340 --> 00:11:19.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm always one to encourage
a test that requires teamwork,</b></Default>

c0000200
00:11:20.220 --> 00:11:21.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as the current
first-class mages</b></Default>

c0000201
00:11:21.970 --> 00:11:24.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>can't cooperate
to save their lives.</b></Default>

c0000202
00:11:24.350 --> 00:11:25.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We are all ashamed.</b></Default>

c0000203
00:11:26.940 --> 00:11:28.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE]
But among the test-takers</b></Default>

c0000204
00:11:28.940 --> 00:11:31.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is a mage
far too powerful for our exam.</b></Default>

c0000205
00:11:33.690 --> 00:11:35.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You must mean Miss Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000206
00:11:36.820 --> 00:11:38.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because of her help,
many have passed</b></Default>

c0000207
00:11:38.780 --> 00:11:40.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>despite lacking
the requisite strength.</b></Default>

c0000208
00:11:41.410 --> 00:11:43.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We could go through
with a typical third test,</b></Default>

c0000209
00:11:44.290 --> 00:11:46.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but then all the unfit
would lose their lives.</b></Default>

c0000210
00:11:47.540 --> 00:11:48.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sense.</b></Default>

c0000211
00:11:49.130 --> 00:11:51.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You created a trial
that would minimize bloodshed.</b></Default>

c0000212
00:11:52.170 --> 00:11:53.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You don't want that.</b></Default>

c0000213
00:11:54.260 --> 00:11:57.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even I have no desire
to watch pointless slaughter.</b></Default>

c0000214
00:11:57.970 --> 00:11:59.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please forgive me.</b></Default>

c0000215
00:11:59.510 --> 00:12:01.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You don't need to apologize.</b></Default>

c0000216
00:12:01.720 --> 00:12:03.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The fault here
is all Frieren's.</b></Default>

c0000217
00:12:04.890 --> 00:12:06.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>An anomaly warrants an anomaly.</b></Default>

c0000218
00:12:07.350 --> 00:12:09.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Therefore, I will proctor
the third test.</b></Default>

c0000219
00:12:11.400 --> 00:12:13.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It is to be
a peaceful selection.</b></Default>

c0000220
00:12:15.230 --> 00:12:17.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This has been your task
in past years, Lernen.</b></Default>

c0000221
00:12:18.820 --> 00:12:20.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you don't object, do you?</b></Default>

c0000222
00:12:23.030 --> 00:12:25.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your willfulness
is not new to me.</b></Default>

c0000223
00:12:25.240 --> 00:12:27.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you want the test,
you will have it,</b></Default>

c0000224
00:12:27.080 --> 00:12:28.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mistress Serie.</b></Default>

c0000225
00:12:28.830 --> 00:12:30.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It is for the best.</b></Default>

c0000226
00:12:30.420 --> 00:12:32.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am neither worthy
nor qualified</b></Default>

c0000227
00:12:32.460 --> 00:12:33.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to test Miss Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000228
00:12:34.670 --> 00:12:36.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I noticed it at first glance.</b></Default>

c0000229
00:12:36.970 --> 00:12:39.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She seems to be constantly
suppressing her mana.</b></Default>

c0000230
00:12:41.350 --> 00:12:43.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Her well of it is tremendous.</b></Default>

c0000231
00:12:44.220 --> 00:12:46.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It is equal
even to yours, Mistress.</b></Default>

c0000232
00:12:48.640 --> 00:12:49.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000233
00:12:50.190 --> 00:12:52.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me, Falsch,
did you see it?</b></Default>

c0000234
00:12:52.810 --> 00:12:55.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, ma'am,
I saw nothing of the sort.</b></Default>

c0000235
00:12:55.900 --> 00:12:57.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Her mana is great.</b></Default>

c0000236
00:12:57.280 --> 00:12:59.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I could tell that
in the testing area.</b></Default>

c0000237
00:13:00.070 --> 00:13:02.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But to me, it didn't look
like she was suppressing it.</b></Default>

c0000238
00:13:04.240 --> 00:13:05.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There was no fluctuation.</b></Default>

c0000239
00:13:05.910 --> 00:13:07.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was effortless and steady.</b></Default>

c0000240
00:13:08.290 --> 00:13:09.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Every living creature
that has mana</b></Default>

c0000241
00:13:09.910 --> 00:13:12.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>experiences some level
of fluctuation.</b></Default>

c0000242
00:13:12.290 --> 00:13:13.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's inescapable.</b></Default>

c0000243
00:13:14.090 --> 00:13:15.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even if it were
possible to hide,</b></Default>

c0000244
00:13:16.170 --> 00:13:18.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it would take an extraordinary
amount of time to master.</b></Default>

c0000245
00:13:19.220 --> 00:13:21.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Expertise in such a thing
is hardly practical.</b></Default>

c0000246
00:13:23.470 --> 00:13:25.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE]
Frieren has devoted her life</b></Default>

c0000247
00:13:25.390 --> 00:13:28.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to developing
that impractical expertise</b></Default>

c0000248
00:13:28.810 --> 00:13:30.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in order to deceive demons.</b></Default>

c0000249
00:13:32.230 --> 00:13:33.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sipping]</b></Default>

c0000250
00:13:34.110 --> 00:13:36.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Demons are acutely
aware of mana,</b></Default>

c0000251
00:13:36.530 --> 00:13:38.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>far more so than
humans or elves.</b></Default>

c0000252
00:13:39.150 --> 00:13:41.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Unless you are born
with some innate talent,</b></Default>

c0000253
00:13:41.530 --> 00:13:44.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>fooling them requires
centuries of practice.</b></Default>

c0000254
00:13:44.370 --> 00:13:45.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A great skill to have, sure.</b></Default>

c0000255
00:13:46.620 --> 00:13:48.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But an undoubted waste of time.</b></Default>

c0000256
00:13:49.580 --> 00:13:51.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You would become
far more powerful</b></Default>

c0000257
00:13:51.250 --> 00:13:53.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>devoting your efforts
to training something else.</b></Default>

c0000258
00:13:54.210 --> 00:13:56.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's incredibly inefficient.</b></Default>

c0000259
00:13:57.000 --> 00:13:59.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That said, inefficiency
can trick the enemy</b></Default>

c0000260
00:14:00.050 --> 00:14:01.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>into dropping their guard.</b></Default>

c0000261
00:14:02.300 --> 00:14:05.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In a battle between
experienced mages,</b></Default>

c0000262
00:14:05.220 --> 00:14:07.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a slight miscalculation
of your opponent's mana</b></Default>

c0000263
00:14:07.600 --> 00:14:09.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>could be a death sentence.</b></Default>

c0000264
00:14:11.140 --> 00:14:13.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren's techniques
are relatively unpolished</b></Default>

c0000265
00:14:13.480 --> 00:14:14.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>given her great age,</b></Default>

c0000266
00:14:15.440 --> 00:14:17.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>yet she has defeated
countless demons.</b></Default>

c0000267
00:14:19.150 --> 00:14:20.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is her genius.</b></Default>

c0000268
00:14:20.820 --> 00:14:23.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren is truly a master
of controlling mana.</b></Default>

c0000269
00:14:24.320 --> 00:14:26.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If the legends are true,
only the Demon King</b></Default>

c0000270
00:14:27.030 --> 00:14:29.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>could see through her act
at first glance.</b></Default>

c0000271
00:14:30.580 --> 00:14:34.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That is, until you first
beheld her, Lernen.</b></Default>

c0000272
00:14:36.290 --> 00:14:37.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Simply a coincidence.</b></Default>

c0000273
00:14:37.840 --> 00:14:40.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I happened to be there
for a minor fluctuation.</b></Default>

c0000274
00:14:40.920 --> 00:14:42.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nothing more than that.</b></Default>

c0000275
00:14:43.340 --> 00:14:45.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just as modest
as you are dependable.</b></Default>

c0000276
00:14:47.260 --> 00:14:50.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's been over half a century
since you gained your title,</b></Default>

c0000277
00:14:51.180 --> 00:14:53.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the first first-class mage.</b></Default>

c0000278
00:14:54.940 --> 00:14:57.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Decades later, and you're still
the same timid boy.</b></Default>

c0000279
00:15:00.190 --> 00:15:01.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That makes it all
the more regrettable.</b></Default>

c0000280
00:15:01.900 --> 00:15:03.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door creaking]</b></Default>

c0000281
00:15:03.570 --> 00:15:06.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have reached a level
few can ever hope to attain,</b></Default>

c0000282
00:15:06.700 --> 00:15:09.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>only toward the end
of your days.</b></Default>

c0000283
00:15:10.490 --> 00:15:12.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would like to see you
fight Frieren,</b></Default>

c0000284
00:15:12.790 --> 00:15:14.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I doubt
you'll ever get the chance.</b></Default>

c0000285
00:15:16.080 --> 00:15:18.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even if it is a battle
you could win.</b></Default>

c0000286
00:15:21.090 --> 00:15:23.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I must learn
not to take on human students.</b></Default>

c0000287
00:15:24.220 --> 00:15:25.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door creaking]</b></Default>

c0000288
00:15:25.930 --> 00:15:27.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE]
It's always disappointing.</b></Default>

c0000289
00:15:27.720 --> 00:15:28.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door closes]</b></Default>

c0000290
00:15:30.010 --> 00:15:31.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He may have caught Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000291
00:15:31.770 --> 00:15:33.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But after a lifetime beside me,</b></Default>

c0000292
00:15:34.600 --> 00:15:37.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he still can't see
my fluctuations.</b></Default>

c0000293
00:15:39.230 --> 00:15:41.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FALSCH]
For the third and final test,</b></Default>

c0000294
00:15:41.480 --> 00:15:44.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you are all to be interviewed
by Serie the Great Mage.</b></Default>

c0000295
00:15:45.070 --> 00:15:46.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, it's come to this?</b></Default>

c0000296
00:15:46.780 --> 00:15:48.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have no doubt
Serie is intending</b></Default>

c0000297
00:15:48.620 --> 00:15:50.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to fail the both of us.</b></Default>

c0000298
00:15:50.200 --> 00:15:51.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You say that like you know her.</b></Default>

c0000299
00:15:52.160 --> 00:15:53.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I used to.</b></Default>

c0000300
00:15:53.870 --> 00:15:55.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She will let
her intuition guide</b></Default>

c0000301
00:15:55.370 --> 00:15:56.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who passes and who fails.</b></Default>

c0000302
00:15:57.960 --> 00:16:00.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Serie's instincts about
these things are always right.</b></Default>

c0000303
00:16:01.290 --> 00:16:02.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The fact of the matter</b></Default>

c0000304
00:16:02.710 --> 00:16:04.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is that I still have
not grown into the mage</b></Default>

c0000305
00:16:04.760 --> 00:16:06.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she wished for me to become.</b></Default>

c0000306
00:16:07.590 --> 00:16:09.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens]</b></Default>

c0000307
00:16:10.470 --> 00:16:12.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door creaking]</b></Default>

c0000308
00:16:12.350 --> 00:16:19.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000309
00:16:33.490 --> 00:16:34.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000310
00:16:34.700 --> 00:16:39.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000311
00:16:40.830 --> 00:16:43.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Excuse me.
-You have failed the test.</b></Default>

c0000312
00:16:43.290 --> 00:16:44.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Begone.</b></Default>

c0000313
00:16:45.590 --> 00:16:47.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>May I at least ask you why?</b></Default>

c0000314
00:16:48.300 --> 00:16:50.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's clear the presence
of my mana</b></Default>

c0000315
00:16:50.180 --> 00:16:51.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>has all but petrified you.</b></Default>

c0000316
00:16:52.260 --> 00:16:54.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know the limits
of your own abilities well.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:16:56.020 --> 00:16:59.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can't even imagine yourself
as a first-class mage, can you?</b></Default>

c0000318
00:17:00.650 --> 00:17:02.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In the world of magic,</b></Default>

c0000319
00:17:02.310 --> 00:17:04.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that which can't be visualized
cannot be.</b></Default>

c0000320
00:17:05.730 --> 00:17:07.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's fundamental, now go.</b></Default>

c0000321
00:17:08.950 --> 00:17:09.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You fail.</b></Default>

c0000322
00:17:10.200 --> 00:17:11.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You fail.</b></Default>

c0000323
00:17:11.450 --> 00:17:12.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You fail.</b></Default>

c0000324
00:17:12.660 --> 00:17:13.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You fail.</b></Default>

c0000325
00:17:16.200 --> 00:17:17.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000326
00:17:17.960 --> 00:17:20.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just like your peers,
you can't imagine yourself</b></Default>

c0000327
00:17:20.160 --> 00:17:22.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as a first-class mage either.</b></Default>

c0000328
00:17:22.880 --> 00:17:25.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But your reasoning
is different than theirs.</b></Default>

c0000329
00:17:27.460 --> 00:17:29.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're convinced
there's no instance</b></Default>

c0000330
00:17:29.260 --> 00:17:30.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in which I allow you to pass.</b></Default>

c0000331
00:17:31.340 --> 00:17:32.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, am I wrong?</b></Default>

c0000332
00:17:34.220 --> 00:17:36.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll give you a single chance.</b></Default>

c0000333
00:17:36.430 --> 00:17:38.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me your favorite spell.</b></Default>

c0000334
00:17:38.810 --> 00:17:40.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It creates a field of flowers.</b></Default>

c0000335
00:17:43.230 --> 00:17:45.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's the spell
that Flamme taught you.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:17:46.230 --> 00:17:47.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And it's utterly foolish.</b></Default>

c0000337
00:17:48.230 --> 00:17:49.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You fail.</b></Default>

c0000338
00:17:50.280 --> 00:17:51.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course.</b></Default>

c0000339
00:17:56.030 --> 00:17:57.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You would let me mock you?</b></Default>

c0000340
00:17:57.870 --> 00:17:59.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Haven't you learned
to stand your ground?</b></Default>

c0000341
00:18:00.500 --> 00:18:02.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I find it incredibly hard
to believe</b></Default>

c0000342
00:18:02.330 --> 00:18:05.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that a mage like you
defeated the Demon King.</b></Default>

c0000343
00:18:07.880 --> 00:18:09.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
I didn't defeat anything alone.</b></Default>

c0000344
00:18:10.720 --> 00:18:14.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Himmel, Eisen, Heiter, and me.</b></Default>

c0000345
00:18:14.930 --> 00:18:16.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If any one of us
hadn't been there,</b></Default>

c0000346
00:18:16.430 --> 00:18:17.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we couldn't have won.</b></Default>

c0000347
00:18:18.260 --> 00:18:20.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, you had strong allies.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:18:20.810 --> 00:18:21.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How lucky.</b></Default>

c0000349
00:18:23.270 --> 00:18:24.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That I was.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:18:24.770 --> 00:18:25.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Incredibly so.</b></Default>

c0000351
00:18:28.520 --> 00:18:29.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Say, Himmel?</b></Default>

c0000352
00:18:30.440 --> 00:18:32.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of all people,
why did you recruit me?</b></Default>

c0000353
00:18:34.320 --> 00:18:36.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because this party
needed a powerful mage.</b></Default>

c0000354
00:18:37.370 --> 00:18:39.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The capital is full
of powerful mages.</b></Default>

c0000355
00:18:40.410 --> 00:18:41.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You didn't have to choose me.</b></Default>

c0000356
00:18:42.500 --> 00:18:44.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You were the only one
that I wanted.</b></Default>

c0000357
00:18:45.210 --> 00:18:46.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why's that?</b></Default>

c0000358
00:18:46.920 --> 00:18:48.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL] Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000359
00:18:48.090 --> 00:18:50.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though I'm sure it made
no lasting impression on you,</b></Default>

c0000360
00:18:51.170 --> 00:18:54.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the two of us met long ago,
for a brief moment.</b></Default>

c0000361
00:18:54.800 --> 00:18:57.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Hm.
I have no recollection of that.</b></Default>

c0000362
00:18:57.220 --> 00:18:58.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Himmel chuckles]
I know you don't.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:18:59.890 --> 00:19:03.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As a kid, I would forage
for herbs in the woods.</b></Default>

c0000364
00:19:03.390 --> 00:19:04.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One night, I got lost.</b></Default>

c0000365
00:19:05.560 --> 00:19:09.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wandered the pitch-black
forest for hours, all alone.</b></Default>

c0000366
00:19:09.570 --> 00:19:11.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was my first encounter
with loneliness.</b></Default>

c0000367
00:19:13.030 --> 00:19:15.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I began to fear I would never
see my village again.</b></Default>

c0000368
00:19:15.910 --> 00:19:18.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000369
00:19:18.910 --> 00:19:20.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL] Just when
I was about to give up,</b></Default>

c0000370
00:19:21.160 --> 00:19:24.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a mysterious elf pointed me
in the direction of home.</b></Default>

c0000371
00:19:24.920 --> 00:19:27.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She acted more
as a trailhead than a friend.</b></Default>

c0000372
00:19:27.670 --> 00:19:30.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not a word of comfort
or encouragement left her lips.</b></Default>

c0000373
00:19:31.090 --> 00:19:34.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In the eyes of a child,
she seemed so cold-hearted.</b></Default>

c0000374
00:19:35.880 --> 00:19:37.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps she sensed my unease,</b></Default>

c0000375
00:19:38.550 --> 00:19:40.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or perhaps she simply did it
on a whim.</b></Default>

c0000376
00:19:40.720 --> 00:19:46.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000377
00:19:46.390 --> 00:19:47.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL] You cast a spell.</b></Default>

c0000378
00:19:48.440 --> 00:19:51.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One that created a field
of flowers all around us.</b></Default>

c0000379
00:19:51.520 --> 00:19:57.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000380
00:19:57.240 --> 00:19:58.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
I thought it was beautiful.</b></Default>

c0000381
00:20:00.200 --> 00:20:01.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was when I learned</b></Default>

c0000382
00:20:01.740 --> 00:20:03.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just how beautiful
magic can be.</b></Default>

c0000383
00:20:03.830 --> 00:20:07.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000384
00:20:07.370 --> 00:20:09.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's probably
a simple coincidence</b></Default>

c0000385
00:20:09.250 --> 00:20:10.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and as foolish as you say.</b></Default>

c0000386
00:20:11.750 --> 00:20:14.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But in a way,
that spell changed my life.</b></Default>

c0000387
00:20:14.670 --> 00:20:17.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After all, it's what brought
my companions and me together.</b></Default>

c0000388
00:20:20.550 --> 00:20:21.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Also, Serie?</b></Default>

c0000389
00:20:22.640 --> 00:20:24.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have no doubt that you
came into this planning</b></Default>

c0000390
00:20:24.810 --> 00:20:26.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to fail Fern as well.</b></Default>

c0000391
00:20:26.810 --> 00:20:28.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I don't think you will.</b></Default>

c0000392
00:20:30.310 --> 00:20:33.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That girl will surely
exceed your expectations.</b></Default>

c0000393
00:20:34.280 --> 00:20:36.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The era of humans has arrived.</b></Default>

c0000394
00:20:40.410 --> 00:20:42.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE]
Exceed my expectations?</b></Default>

c0000395
00:20:43.030 --> 00:20:45.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The sight of my mana
has her frozen in place.</b></Default>

c0000396
00:20:46.370 --> 00:20:48.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's no different
from the rest of them.</b></Default>

c0000397
00:20:50.830 --> 00:20:51.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000398
00:20:54.920 --> 00:20:55.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold on.</b></Default>

c0000399
00:20:56.260 --> 00:20:58.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me, what is it you see?</b></Default>

c0000400
00:20:58.800 --> 00:21:02.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000401
00:21:03.930 --> 00:21:05.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] It's fluctuating.</b></Default>

c0000402
00:21:09.390 --> 00:21:10.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE] Fern, was it?</b></Default>

c0000403
00:21:12.020 --> 00:21:14.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Join me, become my apprentice.</b></Default>

c0000404
00:21:15.150 --> 00:21:16.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, no, thanks.</b></Default>

c0000405
00:21:22.740 --> 00:21:24.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE] Not only
would I treat you well,</b></Default>

c0000406
00:21:25.870 --> 00:21:27.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd take you far.</b></Default>

c0000407
00:21:27.450 --> 00:21:29.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To heights
you never thought possible.</b></Default>

c0000408
00:21:31.460 --> 00:21:34.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Accept my offer,
and you will ascend to a level</b></Default>

c0000409
00:21:34.460 --> 00:21:36.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>no mage ever has before.</b></Default>

c0000410
00:21:39.510 --> 00:21:42.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does my answer affect
whether or not I pass?</b></Default>

c0000411
00:21:43.050 --> 00:21:44.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It very well might.</b></Default>

c0000412
00:21:48.140 --> 00:21:49.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I understand.</b></Default>

c0000413
00:21:51.520 --> 00:21:52.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mistress Serie?</b></Default>

c0000414
00:21:56.820 --> 00:22:01.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000415
00:22:01.860 --> 00:22:02.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Fern.</b></Default>

c0000416
00:22:03.160 --> 00:22:05.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have a feeling
Serie will make you a proposal.</b></Default>

c0000417
00:22:06.370 --> 00:22:08.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You do not have to accept
her demands.</b></Default>

c0000418
00:22:09.700 --> 00:22:12.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just as Serie will fail me
no matter what I say,</b></Default>

c0000419
00:22:13.500 --> 00:22:16.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she will pass you
regardless of your words.</b></Default>

c0000420
00:22:17.880 --> 00:22:20.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like I said, Serie's intuition
is always right.</b></Default>

c0000421
00:22:22.630 --> 00:22:24.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] I have a teacher...</b></Default>

c0000422
00:22:24.760 --> 00:22:26.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and it's Mistress Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000423
00:22:26.640 --> 00:22:30.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000424
00:22:30.980 --> 00:22:32.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000425
00:22:33.980 --> 00:22:35.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She warned you
this would happen.</b></Default>

c0000426
00:22:36.610 --> 00:22:38.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whatever the case,
I'm not foolish enough</b></Default>

c0000427
00:22:38.940 --> 00:22:40.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to hold back a promising mage.</b></Default>

c0000428
00:22:42.950 --> 00:22:44.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You pass.</b></Default>

c0000429
00:22:48.410 --> 00:22:49.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Next.</b></Default>

c0000430
00:24:20.040 --> 00:24:23.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000431
00:24:28.800 --> 00:24:29.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] I'll see you later.</b></Default>

